            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>水果每天吃得越多越好吗？吃多少最合适？<br><br>《中国居民膳食指南 (2022) 》指出，健康成年人每天摄入200-350克水果比较适宜，并且建议每日选择2-3个品种合理搭配，营养互补。<br><br>这个克数怎么拿捏呢？🤏🏻<br><br>一个中等大小的苹果，去核大约200克，一个去皮的猕猴桃，大约100克，一根去皮的香蕉，大约120克。（卫宝们达标了吗？我远超了…<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（健康中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hly0ckl8hxg206o06owpn.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
